		" 
			>
			<DIV></DIV>
<P>Make a special zone open to the pvp servers only that is server vs server pvp.&nbsp; This is only open to all the servers one day a week.&nbsp; So we all go in there and we fight the other servers and points are scored per server for each kill made by someone from that server.&nbsp; At the end of the day the points are tallied and whichever server has the most points gets to "raid/exp" in that zone for the next week.&nbsp; Make the drops in that zone significant so that everyone WANTS to go to that zone to pvp&nbsp;for a day, but you only get to go pve there for drops&nbsp;if your server wins.&nbsp; If the pve loot is juicy enough a lot of people would participate on the pvp day.</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
