		" 
			>
			I have a question about the suggested changes to the team server.  Will un-guilded players be able to pvp?  It sounded like pvp will be restricted to players who are in guilds, and I don't think that's a good idea.  Simply removing team restrictions so that any race can pvp any race would solve any problems caused by the team system - basically just get rid of the teams.  That way, if people wanted a one race guild they can do so voluntarily but wouldn't be immune to pvp by an un-guilded character of the same race.	
