		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV>In all respects, Me , including many of my associates that i play eq with veto an " Old school " , or Pre luclin , Velious , or kunark server.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>EQ is not for casual players anymore. Sony releases too many expansions for casual players to keep up with. I personally only get 2-3 hours a night , 3-5 times a week to play eq. And thats still alot of time to spend on a computer when you have things in life to deal with. Alot of people are like this, alot of people have play times like this. It seems that sony is only focusing on people who have 12+ hours a day to spend on eq ( The majority of eq ). Where they really dont stop to look at what others who dont , need and want. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Everquest past luclin was not made for pvp. Just look at the in balencing. Anyone can see it. And everyone hates it. I dont know about much of anyone else, but all i get are headaches when i play everquest anymore. Its just honestly not fun =/ when everything is done for you ( Pok Books , Zones with 50% Xp Modifiers ). </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Everquest seems to be turning into The Real World as we know it. It seems that everything now in the real world, is want want want, need need need, give me give me give me. If nothing can be done in under 2 minutes its crap, if you actually have to work for something its crap. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Everquest just keeps getting lazier and lazier. And thats whats going to make alot of these long time players quit. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>PvP is fun, its exciting , its breathtaking.... All before luclin came out.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Please Sony , Release a PvP Classic Server. Its what people want. Its what people are willing to re suscribe and pay for. You havnt given it a try yet. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Discord was a failure , You release a server thats old school set, with a zero tolerance of death, and you only release it for 30 days. Calling it a promotional server. What is that ? Just cause people didnt like the Zero Tolerance Death policy and left means that nobody would stay on a classic server? </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>People have been fighting w/ you guys for years to release a classic server. Would you just give the PEOPLE what they want?</DIV>	
		</td></tr>
